      "message": "There is no point in calling `maybeOwnerWithAutoApprovedVote` as the only useful method is calling, which can be inlined here.\n\n\n\n```suggestion\n    if (!AutoOwnersApproval.applies(\n            ownerId,\n            ownerId,\n            ownerId,\n            filesTouchedByChangeOwner,\n            filesTouchedByChangeOwner,\n            this,\n            changeData.project(),\n            changeData.change().getDest().branch())) {\n      return Set.of();\n    }\n```",
