      "writtenOn": "2026-04-15T21:48:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It looks like the purpose of this method is to look for a pattern in a stream of approvals. Why not simply expose a pure function then and have the caller use it on the stream?\n\nProcessing the stream has side effects of advancing it; therefore, it\u0027s dangerous to pass it as a pure parameter.",
